KT: How are you?

00:02:20.098 --> 00:02:21.947
Keith Barry: Kathryn, it's Keith here.

00:02:21.971 --> 00:02:24.976
I'm going to take you
to a secret location, OK?

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:27.964
