you could see through that blindfold.

00:02:27.988 --> 00:02:30.776
KT: OK, but don't say my name like that.
KB: But you're OK?

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:31.876
KT: Yes.

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:33.976
KB: No way to see through it?
KT: No.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.275
KB: I'll take it off.

00:02:35.299 --> 00:02:36.976
