00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.276
Take it off, you're OK.
We'll stop for a second.

00:02:39.300 --> 00:02:41.348
KT: I'm so afraid
of what I'm going to see.

00:02:41.372 --> 00:02:44.048
KB: You're fine, take it off.
You're OK. You're safe.

00:02:44.072 --> 00:02:45.976
Have you ever heard of second sight?

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.036
KT: No.

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:49.432
KB: Second sight is whereby
a mind-control expert

00:02:49.456 --> 00:02:51.976
can see through somebody else's eyes.

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.000
And I'm going to try that right now.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.000
KT: God.

00:03:06.976 --> 00:03:07.976
KB: Are you ready?

00:03:09.535 --> 00:03:11.976
