00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.000
KT: (Beep)

00:03:17.222 --> 00:03:18.750
KT: Oh, my God!

00:03:18.774 --> 00:03:19.976
KB: Don't say anything,

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.572
