I can't see.

00:03:22.596 --> 00:03:24.263
KT: There's a wall, there's a wall.

00:03:24.287 --> 00:03:26.263
KB: Look at the road, look at the road.

00:03:26.287 --> 00:03:27.976
KT: OK, OK, OK. Oh, my God!

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.976
KB: Now, anything coming at all?
KT: No.

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.039
KB: Sure there's not?

00:03:31.063 --> 00:03:33.276
KT: No, no, I'm just still
looking at the road.

00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:35.176
I'm looking at the road, all the time.

00:03:35.199 --> 00:03:36.975
I'm not taking my eyes off the road.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.000
(Beep)

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.000
(Beep)

00:03:46.993 --> 00:03:48.000
(Beep)

00:03:48.976 --> 00:03:49.976
KT: Oh, my God!

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.001
KB: Where are we? Where are we?

00:03:52.025 --> 00:03:53.930
We're going uphill, are we going uphill?

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.976
KT: Look at the road -- (Beep)

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:58.976
Still got that goddamn blindfold on.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.079
KB: What?

00:04:00.103 --> 00:04:01.745
KT: How are you doing this?

00:04:01.769 --> 00:04:03.579
KB: Just don't break my concentration.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:09.356
We're OK, though?
KT: Yes.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:16.976
That's so weird.

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:20.000
We're nearly there. Oh, my God!

00:04:22.550 --> 00:04:24.737
Oh, my God!

00:04:26.055 --> 00:04:27.678
KB: And I've stopped.

00:04:28.666 --> 00:04:30.330
KT: That is weird.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:37.977
You're like a freak-ass of nature.

00:04:38.001 --> 00:04:40.976
That was the most scary thing
I've ever done in my life!

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:42.048
(Applause)

00:04:42.072 --> 00:04:43.976
KB: Thank you.

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:46.976
By the way, two days ago,
we were going to film this

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:49.976
down there, at the race course,
and we got a guy into a car,

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.976
and we got a camera man in the back,

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:53.537
but halfway through the drive,

00:04:53.561 --> 00:04:56.007
